Sword Art Online Realizes New Story Trailer
05.02.2016
ZACK WEBSTERNEWS REPORTER
Bandai Namco has released a new trailer for Sword Art Online: Hollow Realization, the fourth game for the series. The trailer, along with showing off more gameplay, presents a character named Premiere, an NPC shrouded in mystey.
Hollow Realization will arrive worldwide for PlayStation 4 and PlayStation Vita some time in fall 2016. The game takes place four years after Hollow Fragment in a virtual-reality MMORPG called Sword Art: Origins, which is built on the servers of the original Sword Art Online game.
